Package: hatcloud
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You] 
Depends: ruby, git
Section: security
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/HatBashBR/HatCloud
Description: CloudFlare detector and information gatherer
 HatCloud identifies websites protected by CloudFlare and extracts
 origin server IPs. Useful for bypassing CloudFlare protections
 during security assessments.
